{"tid":93701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上官小強死左","createTime":"2017-01-24T15:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T16:19:56.000Z","uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b260fb6fa54b1a8103c4f1054dd24d76cf1d8b4f","tid":93701,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:30:39.000Z","msg":"天妒英才。<br />\n<br />\n香港著名漫畫《壽星仔》作者上官小強離世 終年66歲<br />\n<br />\n香港著名漫畫《壽星仔》原作者上官小強本月13日因病逝世，終年66歲，遺孀在社交網宣佈死訊，定於下月11日在紅磡世界殯儀館明愛堂設靈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/233038_67c39290ccb3592cfbfbe19472929c16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F233038_67c39290ccb3592cfbfbe19472929c16.jpg&h=501fec11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cae94e1ebdb4c6166097b52db707e2ef2848e5da","tid":93701,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"7286074e63f841c856a8abd0aeb24d5315faada7","tid":93701,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:37:31.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"41406a7452c2899d0200aa39b1ffc9c3d78ac116","tid":93701,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"Oh"},{"pid":"2b654e2191fd82df3840dcc94471d87addb7524a","tid":93701,"uid":50412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:19:56.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}